it World</span></strong><td><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"> 365</span></strong></tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Characteristics of Spirits<td> 365</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Negotiating with Spirits<td> 365</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Bound Spirits<td> 366</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Spirit Combat<td> 366</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; The Spirit World<td> 371</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Spirit Cults<td> 377</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Sample Spirit Cults<td> 379</tr><tr><td><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">Sorcery</span></strong><td><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"> 381</span></strong></tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; The Nature of Sorcery<td> 381</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Sorcery Use<td> 381</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Runes<td> 381</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Manipulating Spells<td> 385</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Casting Spells<td> 386</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Sympathetic Magic<td> 387</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Learning Sorcery<td> 387</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Learning New Spells<td> 389</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Memorizing Spells<td> 390</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Creating New Spells<td> 390</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Increasing Spell Casting Ability<td> 390</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Sample Sorcery Spells<td> 390</tr><tr><td><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">Equipment &amp; Wealth</span></strong><td><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">403</span></strong></tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Standard of Living<td> 403</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Retinues<td> 404</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; The Hide of Land<td> 404</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Temples<td> 406</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Casting Spells<td> 406</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Taxes<td> 407</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Ransom<td> 407</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; The Market<td> 408</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Gifts<td> 408</tr><tr><td>&nbsp; &nbsp; Price List of Goods and Services<td> 408</tr><tr><td><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"